{"tid":1480939,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"［權貴怕攬炒］唐英年：若果「剛愎自用」兼「勇往直前」，為反對而反對，就會容易「車毀人亡」","createTime":"2019-08-17T13:37:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-17T18:58:51.000Z","uid":25229,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1a13a2ab4149c15422fbb12318f93dbc72466427","tid":1480939,"uid":25229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T13:37:04.000Z","msg":"咁多年後睇返，原來唐唐當年都走得好前<br />\n多謝咁多位年輕人為香港走到咁遠 迫到權貴怕攬炒<br />\n請受80後一拜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就算自己有車有樓 但一啲都唔怕攬炒<br />\n如果可以還返個香港俾香港人 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">攬炒又如何</span></span><br />\n<br />\n8.18 香港人加油<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n<br />\n唐英年以名為「跨世代的溝通是我們的共同責任」的演說，發表對80後社運青年之論點，可被稱為「唐五點」，其重點可歸納為：<br />\n<br />\n妥協是民主的產物；<br />\n批評80後社運青年不問青紅皂白，只要是涉及政府及商界的事情歸就會被標籤成利益輸送、官商勾結；<br />\n指摘80後重權利而忽略責任，「不能關起門來當皇帝」；<br />\n警惕80後若果「剛愎自用」兼「勇往直前」，為反對而反對，就會容易「車毀人亡」；<br />\n指摘行動派青年的衝擊手法，擔心會「引致流血」外，香港長此下去會「走上不歸路」。<br />\n<br />\n延伸閱讀<br />\n<br />\n網民反應<br />\n<br />\n香港討論區<br />\n<br />\n香港討論區的討論集中於論壇版塊香港及世界新聞討論，網民大多批評唐英年，甚至有人認為應該控告唐恐嚇，但有部份網民也質疑當中官商勾結的論據。<br />\n<br />\nUwants討論區<br />\n<br />\nUwants討論區的論壇版塊「八十後」現象及時事新聞報導討論均有網民轉貼新聞及討論，其中網民的意見不一[來源請求]。<br />\n<br />\n再延伸閱讀<br />\n<a href=\"https://evchk.wikia.org/zh/wiki/車毀人亡\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fevchk.wikia.org%2Fzh%2Fwiki%2F%E8%BB%8A%E6%AF%80%E4%BA%BA%E4%BA%A1&d=9fV5YN%2BdLeg0vJDpI0pnmlhCriQ9KcwZROA2Rh0I8Zw%3D&h=f6a0907a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://evchk.wikia.org/zh/wiki/車毀人亡</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/唐英年車毀人亡的故事\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2F%E5%94%90%E8%8B%B1%E5%B9%B4%E8%BB%8A%E6%AF%80%E4%BA%BA%E4%BA%A1%E7%9A%84%E6%95%85%E4%BA%8B&d=9fV5YN%2BdLeg0vJDpI0pnmlhCriQ9KcwZROA2Rh0I8Zw%3D&h=1504d2e0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2F%E5%94%90%E8%8B%B1%E5%B9%B4%E8%BB%8A%E6%AF%80%E4%BA%BA%E4%BA%A1%E7%9A%84%E6%95%85%E4%BA%8B&h=6aaa1e48\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/唐英年車毀人亡的故事</a>"},{"pid":"46b9f49ab71e28784a3a29bc298843aaae34dbaa","tid":1480939,"uid":25229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T13:41:48.000Z","msg":"自推俾2011年未出世嘅巴絲睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16c266bbb51ed59f6391e73d2dafa7c836a31f56","tid":1480939,"uid":138288,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T13:43:00.000Z","msg":"屌你，成日用攬炒兇鳩我<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n屋我又買唔起，職又冇份升，份撚屌工得果萬零蚊，我都無野可以炒，話撚知你核彈炒，驚閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4174baaffd3323a1004bf3da071284cbd3d515a6","tid":1480939,"uid":261455,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T13:45:03.000Z","msg":"由頭到尾 我怕嘅只有連攬炒都做唔到"},{"pid":"ab64850512e5f2ee1448c260067f779e419c26e1","tid":1480939,"uid":25229,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"16c266bbb51ed59f6391e73d2dafa7c836a31f56","tid":1480939,"uid":138288,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T13:43:00.000Z","msg":"屌你，成日用攬炒兇鳩我<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n屋我又買唔起，職又冇份升，份撚屌工得果萬零蚊，我都無野可以炒，話撚知你核彈炒，驚閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T14:15:10.000Z","msg":"攬炒只有1%嘅人驚<br />\n99%嘅人不論窮人定中產都唔會係最傷<br />\n<br />\n不怕攬炒 還我香港"},{"pid":"2708093b9ee4156f6e43b3548f122997479e2928","tid":1480939,"uid":25229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T18:45:33.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"535d151d4cd7142a5f5b40d54482914d8e501787","tid":1480939,"uid":262342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4174baaffd3323a1004bf3da071284cbd3d515a6","tid":1480939,"uid":261455,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T13:45:03.000Z","msg":"由頭到尾 我怕嘅只有連攬炒都做唔到"},"citedBy":0,"re